Great American Coffee Taste Test

Erica Galvan

2024-11-26

Introduction

  • Coffee expert, “World Champion Barista” and Youtuber ‘James Hoffman’ partnered with Cometeer, a flash frozen coffee pod delivery service.
  • Live coffee taste test held on Youtube. Viewers who participated were asked to fill out a survey based on 4 coffee samples they received.

  • Link to Github: https://github.com/rfordatascience/tidytuesday/blob/master/data/2024/2024-05-14/readme.md

  • Survey was voluntary

  • Taste test was a follow along live stream. Essentially everyone who participated had the same tasting experience.

What is the preference between Coffee A, B, or C?

coffee_survey %>% 
  filter(!is.na(prefer_abc)) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = prefer_abc, fill = prefer_abc)) + 
  geom_bar() + 
  geom_text(stat = "count", aes(label = ..count..), vjust = -0.5) +
  scale_fill_manual(values = c("tan", "tan3", "saddlebrown")) +
  labs(title = "Coffee Preference: A, B, or C?", 
       x = NULL,
       y = "Count") 
## Warning: The dot-dot notation (`..count..`) was deprecated in ggplot2 3.4.0.

What is the preference between Coffee A or D?

  ggplot(aes(x = prefer_ad, fill = prefer_ad)) + geom_bar() + scale_fill_manual( values = c("tan", "peachpuff3"))+
